  "title": "OpenClaw 彻底改变了产品经理的工作方式：5 个必学用例丨 Aakash Gupta",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzcxMDA5NTI0OA==&mid=2247485394&idx=1&sn=5ef63f67d066b47de9c20331e549a32c",
  "date": "2026-03-19 13:18:00",
  "author": "晚点再听LaterCast",
  "siteName": "晚点再听LaterCast",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=444862e1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FUNwPtic6UWKbmEjTxLAF9uDHYRic4rBGcAK9DWg9tvSgMia4bSjobj1xtSTEevN9skyGibu9z4DR5ydC2GuCibzQ5AMujmuJ2gGBlYkvgM9FOj7M%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <h1 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">我们每天为你更新硅谷最新的 AI 创业与科技播客总结，让你与前沿保持同频。全文约 4000 字，如果暂时没有时间可以试试变成播客<a class=\"weapp_text_link js_weapp_entry\" style=\"\" data-unique-id=\"mmxhgzn2-4bzg73\" data-miniprogram-type=\"text\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wxa4c5894e8895e7d1\" data-miniprogram-path=\"pages/podcast-list/podcast-list\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"晚点再听LaterCast\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-applink=\"#小程序://晚点再听LaterCast/sDVSYFvzcwLGPOf\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">晚点再听LaterCast</span></a></span></h1>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-style: italic;\">“把每天早上的站会简报，放心地交给一行简单的终端命令。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-style: italic;\">“别再当群聊里的“人工路由器”，让 AI 替你决定每一个 Bug 的优先级。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-style: italic;\">“产品经理最大的悲哀，是用最昂贵的脑力，做最廉价的“信息搬运””</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多人将</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, Arial, \\&quot;Noto Sans CJK SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 2em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">OpenClaw</span><span leaf=\"\">视为程序员的专属玩具，但这种认知极大地低估了它的应用边界。事实上，最该为这款工具感到兴奋的，是每天被无数繁杂事务淹没的产品经理。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术专家 Naman Pandey 花费了数周时间，将自己完全沉浸在 OpenClaw 的架构与应用中。他在本期探讨中，他现场演示了将其无缝接入 Slack。最令人瞩目的是，他从零开始构建了五个专为产品经理量身定制的自动化工作流。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们将跟随 Naman 的操作路径，拆解 OpenClaw 的配置陷阱，并深入探讨这五个能够替你接管晨会、监控竞品、分发 Bug 的高价值用例。掌握这些方法，你将从一个疲于奔命的协调者，转变为统筹全局的自动化架构师。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 告别被动问答：为什么产品经理必须拥抱“主动型” Agent？</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">市面上绝大多数的生成式工具，本质上都是被动响应的系统。你抛出一个问题，它给出一个答案，一旦对话窗口关闭，进程就结束了。这种模式在处理独立任务时非常高效，但在应对需要持续跟进、跨系统协作的产品管理工作时，就显得力不从心。产品经理需要的是一个能够自主观察、定时触发并执行复杂逻辑的助手。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenClaw 的核心差异在于它的运行机制。它作为一个守护进程常驻在你的设备上。它拥有持久的记忆，能够跨越不同的会话记住你的偏好与历史指令。更关键的是，它支持基于 Cron 的定时任务。你可以设定它在周日凌晨去抓取数据，在周一早上八点为你生成报告。它不再是一个需要你随时输入指令的打字机，而是一个不知疲倦的虚拟员工。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“在这里，你可以真正掌控你想要做的事情，并占据主动权。你可以设置它执行任务，即使是凌晨三点你在睡觉时，它也能独立运转。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">给读者的收获：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;转变你对人工智能的使用习惯。停止将大模型当作一个高级搜索引擎。梳理你每天或每周必须定时重复执行的任务清单，评估这些任务的逻辑清晰度。只要规则明确，你完全可以将它们转换为 OpenClaw 的定时触发流，把精力从执行层抽离出来。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 消除部署恐惧：三行命令与不可忽视的 Slack 授权细节</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于非技术背景的产品经理来说，看到终端界面往往会产生心理障碍。Naman 在演示中特意强调，OpenClaw 的安装流程已经被极度简化，只需要简单的三个命令：NPM 安装、环境初始化，以及唤醒机器人。在终端窗口中，大量的输出信息会让新手感到恐慌。Naman 给出了一个极其直白的判断标准：只要你没有看到红色的报错字体，一切就都在正常运转。那些黄色的警告信息通常只是依赖项的版本提示，完全可以安全地忽略。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在将 OpenClaw 接入团队最常用的通讯工具 Slack 时，存在一个极其隐蔽且让无数人抓狂的陷阱。很多用户在 Slack API 控制台中配置好了各项权限，回到频道里测试时却发现机器人毫无反应，仿佛坏掉了一样。这是因为权限的变更并不会自动生效。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“如果你没有看到红色的文字，你就没问题。每次在 Slack API 控制台更改机器人权限时，你必须点击‘重新安装到工作区’，否则任何权限更改都不会保留。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">面对技术配置时，掌握抓大放小的原则。不要被繁杂的日志输出干扰判断。在处理任何第三方平台（如 Slack、Jira）的 API 集成时，牢记权限刷新的必要动作。理解这些底层平台的基本授权逻辑，能够极大地减少你排查低级故障的时间。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">3. 用例一与二：从本地知识库到自动化晨会简报</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">产品经理每天要回答无数遍相同的问题：“那个功能的 PRD 在哪？”、“最新版的 FAQ 更新了吗？”。Naman 展示了 OpenClaw 的第一个杀手级用例：将本地文件夹转变为团队的智能知识库。你只需要将所有的产品需求文档、常见问题解答和操作手册拖入本地的 `.openclaw/workspace/docs` 目录中。团队中的任何人只要在 Slack 频道里@这个机器人，它就能瞬间检索整个知识库并给出精准解答，甚至还能根据讨论结果直接将新内容写回这些本地文档中。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二个用例则直接针对每天的晨会。传统的晨会往往耗时且流于形式。通过设定一个基于自然语言描述的定时任务，OpenClaw 会在夜间自动扫描开发团队、支持团队的核心 Slack 频道。到了早上 9 点，它会自动在群里发布一份极其精炼的简报，清晰列出：昨晚发布了什么代码、当前有哪些任务被阻塞、以及客户提出了哪些紧急投诉。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“每天早上 9 点，OpenClaw 会扫描你团队的 Slack 频道。它会总结隔夜发生的事情，识别阻碍因素，并发布一份简明的晨会报告。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">将信息的聚合与分发工作全面自动化。把你的本地电脑变成团队的资料大脑，利用定时任务接管常规的状态同步会议。这能让你把每天早上最清醒的黄金时间，用在思考产品战略上，而不是用来在各个群聊里爬楼看聊天记录。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">4. 用例三：基于客户层级的智能 Bug 路由分发</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">处理无穷无尽的 Bug 反馈，是产品管理中最消耗精力的环节。所有的反馈涌入同一个池子，产品经理需要手动阅读、评估严重程度、判断客户价值，然后再分发给不同的技术团队。这个过程极度依赖人工经验，且极易出错。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Naman 演示的智能 Bug 路由机制，展示了 OpenClaw 跨系统的数据处理能力。当一个新的故障报告进来时，机器人会自动提取报告人的邮箱地址，并去读取一份存储了客户分层信息的本地 CSV 文件。如果发现该邮箱属于支付高昂费用的企业级客户，机器人会立刻将这个 Bug 标记为最高优先级，并直接推送到核心工程团队的专属频道；如果发现该邮箱属于免费层用户，且反馈内容涉及界面问题，它会将其标记为低优先级，并路由给设计团队的待办列表中。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“OpenClaw 读取错误报告，在客户 CSV 文件中查找报告人，立即将企业级错误升级给工程部门，并将免费层错误作为低优先级路由给设计部门。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">利用自动化工具建立一套冷酷且高效的业务分类规则。不要用人力去承担信息分流的快递员角色。梳理你的客户分层数据，将其与任务分发逻辑强绑定。让机器依据商业价值来决定开发团队的响应速度，这是提升资源利用率的关键战术。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">5. 用例四：全天候运行的竞对情报与用户心声雷达</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">市场调研和竞品分析通常是一项周期性的工作，产品经理往往在制定季度规划时才会去集中看一次数据。这种低频的观察会导致你错过市场上的微妙变化。OpenClaw 可以将这种低频动作转化为高频的持续监控。你可以设定机器人每隔 30 分钟去扫描一次竞争对手的官方网站、公开的新闻提及以及应用商店的评价。它会自动梳理出对手的优劣势分析（SWOT），并悄悄发布到你的私人 Slack 频道中。数月积累下来，这种高频采样能让你清晰地看到对手战略方向的演变轨迹。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">同样的逻辑也适用于收集用户心声。用户的抱怨散落在各个角落：Slack 的支持频道、客服邮箱、Google 商店的评价、甚至 Reddit 的论坛帖子里。OpenClaw 能够接入这些所有的数据源，持续聚合信息，并在每周一生成一份全局的用户心声报告。它能准确告诉你本周用户抱怨最多的是哪个具体功能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“OpenClaw 可以每 30 分钟监控一次竞争对手的网站、评论和提及情况，并将 SWOT 分析发布到私有 Slack 频道。它能随着时间的推移跟踪变化，以便几个月后进行趋势分析。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">将你的市场嗅觉外包给算法。建立持续的数据监控管道，用高频的信息采样代替周期性的人工调研。当你拥有一张覆盖全网的实时反馈雷达网时，你在制定产品路线图时将拥有无可辩驳的数据底气。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">6. 用例五：绝不妥协的自动化安全审计</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">当赋予机器人如此强大的读取、写入和跨系统调用权限时，安全问题就成了悬在头顶的利剑。产品经理绝对不能抱有侥幸心理，认为小规模使用就不会出事。Naman 提出的第五个用例，是将安全审计本身变成一项自动化任务。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">你可以直接向 OpenClaw 下达指令，要求它分析自身的安全漏洞。作为一个具备审查能力的代理，它会扫描当前的配置环境，主动向你报告诸如“存在不受限制的文件访问权限”、“防火墙端口被意外关闭”或“缺少关键的审批放行网关”等高危风险。通过设定一个每周执行的 Cron 任务，你可以确保这个安全审计在后台定期运转，防患于未然。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“上线前的安全审计是不容谈判的，告诉 OpenClaw 分析自身的安全漏洞。它会标记不受限制的文件访问、禁用的防火墙和缺失的审批关卡。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在引入任何强大的自动化工具时，必须同步构建制衡机制。让系统自己监督自己，将安全检查作为日常工作流的强制前置条件。永远不要为了追求运行效率而牺牲系统权限的严谨性。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">7. 部署策略与硬件选择：把控制权留在自己手里</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在了解了上述强大的功能后，接下来的决策就是如何部署。Naman 深入探讨了三种常见的运行环境：虚拟专用服务器（VPS）、独立主机（如 Mac Mini）以及本地笔记本电脑。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用 VPS 的最大优势是它能够保证系统 24 小时全天候在线，但这种便利性是有代价的。一旦系统失控或者出现权限滥用，你很难在第一时间进行物理上的切断。相比之下，购置一台专门的 Mac Mini 放在办公室是一个极其推荐的平衡方案，它既能保持常亮，又能让你触手可及。而对于绝大多数刚刚起步的产品经理来说，将系统部署在日常工作的笔记本电脑上其实是最为稳妥的策略。因为它的运行机制与你的工作节奏强绑定，一旦你察觉异常，只需合上电脑屏幕，所有的进程就会被强制休眠。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“VPS 提供全天候的高可用性，但剥夺了你的物理终止开关。在笔记本电脑上进行本地部署是最安全的，因为当你合上电脑时，机器人也会休眠。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在接触具备自主执行能力的代理系统初期，将物理控制权置于绝对在线时长之上。不要盲目追求全天候的自动化。先在完全可控的本地环境中跑通业务逻辑，当你对系统的行为模式建立了足够的信任后，再考虑向云端或独立服务器迁移。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语：成为规则的制定者</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Naman Pandey 通过这五个详尽的用例向我们展示了一个事实：OpenClaw 绝不是一个单纯的代码生成工具，它是一个全能的业务编排系统。对于产品经理而言，这场变革意味着工作重心的彻底转移。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">当你能够熟练运用这些代理工具时，你就不再需要亲自去阅读每一条枯燥的客户反馈，也不需要每天准时上线催促开发进度。你将拥有一个不知疲倦的团队，严格按照你设定的逻辑去运转。去拥抱这些终端命令，去设计那些复杂的监控与路由规则。在这个新纪元里，谁能最好地定义流程、设定边界，谁就能释放出最惊人的生产力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\">内容来源：“The Ultimate OpenClaw Guide For AI PMs”丨Aakash Gupta</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\">原视频：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YLXRg078EKs\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YLXRg078EKs</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文介绍了 OpenClaw 这一 AI Agent 框架在产品管理中的五大实战用例，旨在帮助产品经理从繁琐的事务性工作中解脱，通过自动化工作流实现从“信息搬运工”到“自动化架构师”的转型。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文介绍了 OpenClaw 这一 AI Agent 框架在产品管理中的五大实战用例，旨在帮助产品经理从繁琐的事务性工作中解脱，通过自动化工作流实现从“信息搬运工”到“自动化架构师”的转型。",
  "summary": "文章总结了 Naman Pandey 关于利用 OpenClaw 构建 AI 代理工作流的实战经验。核心观点在于摒弃将 AI 视为“被动问答工具”的传统认知，将其打造为具备持久记忆、定时触发能力的“主动型”助手。文中详细拆解了五个针对产品经理的高价值用例：构建本地知识库、自动化晨会简报、基于客户分层的智能 Bug 路由、全天候竞品与用户心声监控，以及自动化安全审计。此外，文章还探讨了部署策略，强调在追求自动化效率的同时，必须保留物理控制权，并建立系统性的安全制衡机制，为产品经理提供了一套切实可行的 AI 落地路径。",
